            <div id="review_1278213_full_content" class="full-content"></div>
          </div>
        </div>
    </div>
  </div>

      
  



  <div xmlns:v="http://rdf.data-vocabulary.org/#" typeof="v:Review">
    <div class="main review-item" id="1068060">
        

  <header class="main-hd">
    <h3 class="title">
      <a href="https://book.douban.com/review/1068060/" class="title-link">为什么不叫兵不厌诈</a>
      <div class="toggle_review right">        <a href="javascript:;" id="toggle-1068060"class="indicator unfold j" title="展开全文">        </a>
      </div>
    </h3>
    

<div class="header-more">
    <a class="author-avatar" href="https://www.douban.com/people/1040799/"><img width="48" height="48" src="https://img3.doubanio.com/icon/u1040799-1.jpg"></a>
    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/1040799/" class="author">
      <span property="v:reviewer">偷枣小子</span>
    </a>    <span property="v:rating" class="allstar50 main-title-rating" title="力荐"></span>
  <span property="v:dtreviewed" content="2006-08-22"
      class="main-meta">2006-08-22 15:13:04</span>
</div>

  </header>

        <div class="main-bd">
          <div id="review_1068060_short" class="review-short">
            <div class="short-content">
                  我觉得叫兵不厌诈更好。不过，还是挺佩服出版社的责任编辑，竟然跟堂听课。难怪这两年刘心武、易中天火了，火就火在是以讲课的方式引人入胜。反过来讲，大学里的老师真的应该学学他们啦，什么叫好老师？能够让大家听进去就是好老师。否则，学问再深，还不是催眠？

                    <a class="pl" href="https://book.douban.com/review/1068060/#comments">(2回应)</a>
                  <div class="more-info pl clearfix">
                    <span class="left">4有用 / 6没用</span>
                  </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div id="review_1068060_full" class="hidden">
            <div id="review_1068060_full_content" class="full-content"></div>
          </div>
        </div>
    </div>
  </div>





</div>










            <p class="pl" align="right">
                &gt;
                <a href="reviews">
                    更多书评31篇
                </a>
            </p>
</section>
    
